        "subject": "LU-18175 lustre: fix shrinker debugfs support",
        "message": "LU-18175 lustre: fix shrinker debugfs support\n\nIf you have a kernel such that !HAVE_SHRINKER_ALLOC\nand CONFIG_SHRINKER_DEBUG=y, the shrinker code will\nnot compile since \"struct ll_shrinker *s\" will not\nbe defined. Rework the allocation in ll_shrinker_create()\nto fix this.\n\nFixes: 1d6cdb63f3a1 (\"LU-18175 lustre: back port shrinker debugfs support.\")\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: I39edc56299fb77682621691248ceb5a8738bb19a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
